{"tid":1131055,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"紳士實用”上車指南”，日本R18漫畫雜誌故事題材「強姦/和姦傾向」統計","createTime":"2019-04-29T12:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T12:54:07.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae86cbb5e064012bb7077394ce7bd610a7e8fe3","tid":1131055,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/85445/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F85445%2F&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYov2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=b446e8aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/85445/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/00-88.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F00-88.jpg%3F&h=dd4a9348&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紳士實用&rdquo;上車指南&rdquo;，日本R18漫畫雜誌故事題材「強姦/和姦傾向」統計<br />\n作者: 填海紳士 日期: 29/04/2019 ACGN, 新聞動態, 漫畫<br />\n<br />\n關於日本紳士對R18作品的口味，在之前發表的FANZA同人2018年數據報告中可見「NTL・NTR」類別的人氣是壓倒性優勢<br />\n<br />\n男女老幼都愛看NTR，FANZA同人2018年數據報告人氣全面No.1類別：「NTL・NTR」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/75421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F75421&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYov2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=97fbd24b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/75421</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/01-4.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F01-4.png%3F&h=b0d0e0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於商業R18作品領域，最近也有一位&rdquo;R18漫畫統計家&rdquo;公開發表了一份「R18漫畫統計」報告<br />\n這份報告對R18漫畫數據化進行探討，當中就有一份日本R18漫畫雜誌作品題材到底是「強姦傾向」還是「和姦傾向」的統計<br />\n<br />\n統計包涵了日本市場上19部R18漫畫雜誌，結果反映整體而言，<span style=\"color: red;\">在商業領域中接近八成的R18漫畫作品都是「和姦」題材故事</span><br />\n<br />\n牧田翠＠夏コミはアイマス統計本<br />\n@MiDrill<br />\n<strong> 和姦の定義としては「酒や薬物などで判断力を奪っていない」状態で、「暴力、脅迫による強制がない」など、刑法177条の判例を見ながら集計しています。<br />\nどうしても主観は混じる部分はありますので、良い基準を常に探ってはいます。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>這裡說的「和姦」指雙方合意下進行&rdquo;愉悅的行為&rdquo;，在統計中這定義也不包括因用藥等今人失去判斷力的狀況</strong><br />\n<br />\n當然以個別R18漫畫雜誌來說也有以&rdquo;強上弓&rdquo;題材為主的，但也只有兩部雜誌<br />\n<br />\n這個統計對於各界紳士來說也可以視作為實用的&rdquo;上車指南&rdquo;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n「R18漫畫統計」報告在下面推文的連結內<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/HIfIFTycTi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FHIfIFTycTi&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYov2J6e4EmGiVIqwvzORC%2Fw%3D&h=1b7e0213\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/HIfIFTycTi</a><br />\n<br />\n另外補充一提，這裡的文章題圖用的是《COMIC阿吽》2019年6月號封面，由誰繪製的相信大家都知道～(圖的右上角就已經寫了"},{"pid":"f40825521945a115ec0d102ebee1653937c9fd47","tid":1131055,"uid":49275,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"淨係睇純愛路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a77cc9a010f71bf8558c4e5e484a78b58fb763","tid":1131055,"uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f40825521945a115ec0d102ebee1653937c9fd47","tid":1131055,"uid":49275,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"淨係睇純愛路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"純愛太悶"},{"pid":"e8ef2433925ec705d61e39185005fd76fdc4e209","tid":1131055,"uid":18107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"想知男人睇ntr係代入邊個角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fafc828cc01ba2ee964686eb2eb61cb3afe090e","tid":1131055,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8ef2433925ec705d61e39185005fd76fdc4e209","tid":1131055,"uid":18107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"想知男人睇ntr係代入邊個角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"代入女主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" cla